Ossi is a browser based social media application designed to work in Nokia Web Runtime environment in Series 60 operating system as well as in OS X Dashboard. Ossi is developed in the OtaSizzle project by Helsinki Institute for Information Technology HIIT. Ossi utilizes OtaSizzle's Aalto Social Interface for its data storage via a RESTful API.  For additional information contact Jani Turunen / jani.turunen@hiit.fi.
